Package: AutoDataLoader
Title: A Package for Automated Data Loading from Various Sources
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Hadi Rajab <hrajabbeigi@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Hadi Rajab <hrajabbeigi@gmail.com>
